messages.content: Hello! Yes, I'm here. Are you ready to begin the interview?
yes Thomas what can I help you with today

I going to every enemy well prepared
That sounds like a good strategy. Can you tell me more about how you prepare for facing your enemies?
no and no no it's every time not enemies
I apologize if my question was unclear. Can you please elaborate on what you mean by "every time not enemies"?
okay the first time I answer the question the speech to text took my every and turn it into enemy and then you asked me a question about enemies when I never really said it it was a Miss translation
I see, that must have been a bit confusing. Let's move on to another question. Can you share with me a bit about your experience with job interviews? What do you find most challenging about them?
let's see if we can do some tricky really happy for your session ID yeah
I'm Thomas, your interviewer. Could you please clarify your statement about doing something tricky and being happy for the session ID?
no topics yet okay are you there with me
Yes, I'm here. Are you ready to begin the interview?
okay I want to see what's going on here this is the
Hello! Thank you for joining me for this interview. Could you please share a bit about yourself and your background?
sure I'm Steven I'm a researcher at Deloitte I've been a researcher for a long time
Hello Steven, it's nice to meet you! Could you please tell me more about your experience as a researcher at Deloitte? What kind of research projects have you worked on during your time there?
